  "text": "During polymerization, the intensity of light is known to decrease with transmission through the RBCs [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] . Many factors such as filler load and size, shade, opacity, translucency and material thickness can affect light transmission. These factors are overlapped and will be discussed within the following Sections.",
